OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright, sunny start,
OL,6,Fcloud will increase through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Showers move in from the
OL,8,Fnorth from late morning, clearing by
OL,9,Flate afternoon with sunny intervals
OL,10,Ffollowing. Breezy, particularly on
OL,11,Fcoasts, and feeling cool in the
OL,12,Fnortherly winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSunny spells continue through
OL,15,Fthe evening, though it will feel cool
OL,16,Fin a northerly breeze. Largely dry
OL,17,Fovernight, aside from isolated coastal
OL,18,Fshowers, with a widespread frost
OL,19,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
